# 1Ô∏è‚É£8Ô∏è‚É£ GOVERNANCE CONTROLS

Logic 25 enforces:

* Transparent scoring criteria
* No hidden punitive adjustments
* Audit logging of score changes (Logic 14)
* Supplier right to review major changes
* Protection against retaliation scoring

Trust must be data-driven and defensible.

---

